reviewText: Better to buy x ray glasses than to anticipate anything remotely resembling quality 3-D here. Definition is low, colors are dark and muted, at times some type of depth appears where everything else is so dimly flat and faded. Serious collectors should forego this one for more attractive fare.

This DVD has some good 3d anaglyphic scenes .But for 3d fans, these scenes remain behind the "stereo window"...that is, it shows the depth behind the window ( the frame of your TV/Computer )...there is little that " pops out" out of the window, other that the logo title ...you get two DVDs ; one that shows all of Lisa Ann's scenes, the other one has other models including Brittany Andrews and a threesome, otherwise this features all solo performances...about the only thing I wished they could have added was a 2d option to view...that is why I gave it  a 4...
If your a fan of lisa ann you will love this two DVD set. one DVD is devoted to lisa ann and the second DVD have assorted other porn star, including a lesbian threesome.

I bought this item for a bachelor-party for my brother in law as a expensive Joke!
What a boring thing.
